:48:38,234 - asyncio - DEBUG - <asyncio.sslproto.SSLProtocol object at 0x153eeb94f4d0>: SSL handshake took 22.9 ms\n2025-05-17 11:48:38,235 - asyncio - DEBUG - <asyncio.TransportSocket fd=6, family=2, type=1, proto=6, laddr=('10.1.4.3', 47816), raddr=('142.250.184.206', 443)> connected to None:None: (<asyncio.sslproto._SSLProtocolTransport object at 0x153eeb731c10>, <aiohttp.client_proto.ResponseHandler object at 0x153eeb9e8830>)\n2025-05-17 11:48:38,261 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - INFO - Refreshed auth, lounge id token A [redacted]\n2025-05-17 11:48:38,539 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:48:48,550 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:48:53,819 - asyncio - DEBUG - <_SelectorSocketTransport fd=6 read=polling write=<idle, bufsize=0>> received EOF\n2025-05-17 11:48:53,819 - asyncio - DEBUG - <asyncio.sslproto.SSLProtocol object at 0x153eeb94f4d0> received EOF\n2025-05-17 11:48:58,554 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:49:08,564 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:49:18,575 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:49:28,586 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:49:38,597 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:49:48,607 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:49:58,618 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:50:08,621 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Waiting for device to be connected\n2025-05-17 11:50:18,632 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bf