e segment UUID will be sent? (Y/n) y\nDo you want to mute native YouTube ads automatically? (y/N) y\nDo you want to skip native YouTube ads automatically? (y/N) y\nDo you want to enable autoplay? (Y/n) n\nConfig finished\nroot@unraid:~/media/torrents# /usr/bin/docker run -it --rm --name='sponsorblock' --net='mgmt' -e TZ=\"Europe/Berlin\" -e HOST_OS=\"Unraid\" -e HOST_HOSTNAME=\"unraid\" -e HOST_CONTAINERNAME=\"sponsorblock\" --pids-limit 2048 -v '/mnt/user/appdata/sponsorblock/':'/app/data':rw -l net.unraid.docker.icon='https://github.com/ajayyy/SponsorBlock/raw/master/public/icons/LogoSponsorBlocker256px.png' -l net.unraid.docker.managed=dockerman 'ghcr.io/dmunozv04/isponsorblocktv:latest' --debug\n2025-05-17 19:46:43,516 - asyncio - DEBUG - Using selector: EpollSelector\n2025-05-17 19:46:43,521 - iSponsorBlockTV-5nea16bfautufhd7qgrq4nfj2i - DEBUG - Refreshing auth\n2025-05-17 19:46:43,535 - asyncio - DEBUG - Get address info www.youtube.com:443, type=<SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, flags=<AddressInfo.AI_ADDRCONFIG: 32>\n2025-05-17 19:46:43,565 - asyncio - DEBUG - Getting address info www.youtube.com:443, type=<SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, flags=<AddressInfo.AI_ADDRCONFIG: 32> took 29.893ms: [(<AddressFamily.AF_INET: 2>, <SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, 6, 'youtube-ui.l.google.com', ('142.250.186.78', 443)), (<AddressFamily.AF_INET: 2>, <SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, 6, 'youtube-ui.l.google.com', ('142.250.186.142', 443)), (<AddressFamily.AF_INET: 2>, <SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, 6, 'youtube-ui.l.google.com', ('142.250.185.238', 443)), (<AddressFamily.AF_INET: 2>, <SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, 6, 'youtube-ui.l.google.com', ('216.58.206.46', 443)), (<AddressFamily.AF_INET: 2>, <SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, 6, 'youtube-ui.l.google.com', ('142.250.184.206', 443)), (<AddressFamily.AF_INET: 2>, <SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, 6, 'youtube-ui.l.google.com', ('142.250.181.238', 443)), (<AddressFamily.AF_INET: 2>, <SocketKind.SOCK_STREAM: 1>, 6, 'youtube-ui.l.google.com', ('172.217.23.110